  ]
}
```

</details>

### Schedule
Reports are generated on two schedules:

1. Daily, from 0001 UTC
2. Monthly, from 01 0001 UTC


### Webhook
To be notified when a report is ready, subscribe to the `report-completed` webhook topic.

This webhook is sent when report generation has finished for reports you have requested. Refer to the webhook documentation for full payload details.


### Download
To download a report, use the `reportId` from the webhook payload with the file download endpoint.

The endpoint returns a short-lived pre-signed S3 URL that can be used to download the report file.

Download API call example:

```bash
curl -L -X POST 'https://app.immersve.com/api/reports/{reportId}/download'
```
